<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>随笔 on Ivo's Inkwell</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/</link><description>Recent content in 随笔 on Ivo's Inkwell</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 Ivo</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ivoink.qzz.io/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E7%AC%94/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>openclaw(clawbot)部署笔记</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/openclaw-clawbot-deployment/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/openclaw-clawbot-deployment/</guid><description>&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;简述
 &lt;div id="简述" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#%e7%ae%80%e8%bf%b0" aria-label="锚点"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在开始进行部署之前，一定要准备好环境。首先就是Linux，如果是使用Linux系统一定要选择systemd的，要不然部署上会出现网关不可达等一系列问题。在部署的时候出现了很多的问题，重复了很多次，没做截图，所以以下内容只能用文字的形式进行表述。&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/openclaw-clawbot-deployment/featured.png"/></item><item><title>Redmi Note 12T Pro刷PixelOS</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/redmi-note-12t-pro-pixelos/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/redmi-note-12t-pro-pixelos/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;准备工具：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://miuirom.xiaomi.com/rom/u1106245679/7.6.727.43/miflash_unlock_en_7.6.727.43.zip" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;miflash_unlock_en&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://cdn.alsgp0.fds.api.mi-img.com/micomm/MiFlash2020-3-14-0.rar" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;MiFlash&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://share.fnnas.net/s/867ec7a8a4344ca78a" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;PiexlOS刷机包&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;解锁Bootloader
 &lt;div id="解锁bootloader" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#%e8%a7%a3%e9%94%81bootloader" aria-label="锚点"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;需要使用&lt;strong&gt;miflash_unlock&lt;/strong&gt;工具，手机需降级回MIUI14，解锁设备方法：“进入开发者选项 - 设备解锁状态 - 绑定账号”后即可继续。&lt;strong&gt;注：如果解锁工具连接手机后没反应，下载MiFlash打开后点击弹出的安装驱动后再试&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/redmi-note-12t-pro-pixelos/featured.jpg"/></item><item><title>UI设计语言——观Liquid Glass发布感悟</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/ui-design-liquid-glass-thoughts/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/ui-design-liquid-glass-thoughts/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;这个题目其实从一开始Beta版开始的时候就已经起草，但是一直到现在又重新写一遍，其中有我想讲的很多事情。&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/ui-design-liquid-glass-thoughts/featured.jpg"/></item><item><title>2025.10.25反思</title><link>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/2025-10-25-reflection/</link><pubDate>Sat, 25 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/2025-10-25-reflection/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;在参加了TRAE Friends@南京的活动之后，我发现我所缺失的不是代码能力和学习能力，而是对于产品和软件有自己的思考。&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://ivoink.qzz.io/posts/specks/2025-10-25-reflection/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>